            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SIBAR",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The silicon detector",
                "telescope to record recoils deuterons from small-angle",
                "elastic pd scattering. the detector provided an unambig",
                "Deutron identification with a detector resolution of",
                "300 KeV,",
                "and"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "MWPC",
                "MWPC",
                "MWPC",
                "SCIN",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The telescope",
                "comprises a set of three multiwire proportional",
                "chambers and a two-plane scintillation hodoscope,",
                "consisting of vertically oriented counters (eight in",
                "first plane, nine in second). The detector was used to",
                "record a fast proton pair emitted in the forward",
                "direction with small excitation energy (< 3 MeV)."
              ]
            }
          ],
